Images: ["[630_360_16807...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/thumb_files/630_360_1680790514-794.jpg)", "[1680790472-93...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/1680790472-937.jpg)", "[1680790499-98...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/1680790499-989.jpg)"]

Tags: ['Голлівуд', 'Тварини', 'Україна', 'Війна з росією']

